===Verb===

'''to expound'''

#To lay [[open]]; to [[expose]] to [[view]]; to [[examine]].
#To lay open the [[meaning]] of; to [[explain]] or [[discuss]] at length; to [[clear]] of [[obscurity]]; to [[interpret]].
#:''to '''expound''' a text of Scripture, a law, a word, a meaning, or a riddle.''

